description:
Use this tool when you are asked to communicate with another Agent on this system. You can use this tool to list agents (mode=list), describe agents (mode=describe), and execute requests via the A2A protocol.

An example compliant request is as follows:
```
{
    "jsonrpc": "2.0",
    "id": "4",
    "method": "message/send",
    "params": {
        "message": {
            "messageId": "msg-001",
            "role": "user",
            "parts": [
                {
                    "kind": "text",
                    "text": "What knowledge do you have available to you? Please list all knowledge sources, tools, skills, or data you can access."
                }
            ]
        }
    }
}
```
